{"surah": 101, "verses": [{"id": 1, "text": "ٱلْقَارِعَةُ <span class=end>١</span>"}, {"id": 2, "text": "مَا <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْقَارِعَةُ <span class=end>٢</span>"}, {"id": 3, "text": "وَم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</tajweed>كَ مَا <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْقَارِعَةُ <span class=end>٣</span>"}, {"id": 4, "text": "يَوْمَ يَكُونُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed><tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َاسُ كَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْفَرَاشِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>ث<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>ثِ <span class=end>٤</span>"}, {"id": 5, "text": "وَتَكُونُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْجِبَالُ كَ<tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعِهْنِ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْمَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نف</tajweed><tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>شِ <span class=end>٥</span>"}, {"id": 6, "text": "فَأَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َا مَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ث</tajweed>َقُلَتْ مَو<tajweed class=madda_normal>َٲ</tajweed>زِينُهُۥ <span class=end>٦</span>"}, {"id": 7, "text": "فَهُوَ فِى عِيشَ<tajweed class=idgham_wo_ghunnah>ةٍ ر</tajweed>َّاضِيَةٍ <span class=end>٧</span>"}, {"id": 8, "text": "وَأَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َا مَنْ خَفَّتْ مَو<tajweed class=madda_normal>َٲ</tajweed>زِينُهُۥ <span class=end>٨</span>"}, {"id": 9, "text": "فَأُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>ُهُ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ۥ</tajweed> هَاوِيَةٌ <span class=end>٩</span>"}, {"id": 10, "text": "وَم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>دْ</tajweed>رَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ٮٰ</tajweed>كَ مَا هِيَهْ <span class=end>١٠</span>"}, {"id": 11, "text": "نَارٌ حَامِيَةُۢ <span class=end>١١</span>"}]}